        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me ask you a question: how many hours a week do you spend on tasks that are necessary but don't require your unique human touch? Drafting routine emails, logging calls in your CRM, scheduling meetings, and preparing agendas. For most of us, it's a staggering number. We got into our fields to do the creative, strategic work—yet we drown in admin.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://try.lindy.ai/gkd3o3sgd7d2"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That's exactly the problem Lindy solves. It's not just another chatbot. Lindy is a platform of autonomous AI agents you can deploy to handle entire workflows from start to finish, 24/7. Think of it as hiring a highly efficient, always-available virtual assistant, but without the $8,000 monthly price tag of a human one. I've been using it to reclaim my time, and the results have been frankly incredible. **",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start building your own AI team here",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "**.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
