      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Not at all. Lindy provides a library of pre-built agent templates (e.g., for email drafting, CRM updates) that you can deploy in minutes. The interface is designed for business users, not developers. You connect your apps and give the agent instructions in plain English.",
            "marks": []
