        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Lindy operates with enterprise-grade security. You control all permissions and can revoke access at any time. Your data is encrypted, and the AI processes it to perform tasks without storing sensitive information unnecessarily. You are always in control of what your agents can see and do.",
            "marks": []
          }
